					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1703" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1022&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1363&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你能想像一間公司被許多可愛貓咪包圍的景象嗎？國外一間不動產建築公司，因專門設計 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/24/%e8%b2%93%e5%a5%b4%e5%80%91%e7%9a%84%e5%a4%a2%e5%b9%bb%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%ef%bc%9f%e5%9c%a8%e9%80%99%e8%a3%a1%e4%b8%8a%e7%8f%ad%e7%ab%9f%e8%83%bd%e4%ba%ab%e5%8f%97%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9%e8%a2%ab%e8%b2%93/">貓奴們的夢幻公司？在這裡上班竟能享受整天被貓咪包圍！ </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1703" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1022&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1363&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chen-urUcOb5XlyA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你能想像一間公司被許多可愛貓咪包圍的景象嗎？國外一間不動產建築公司，因專門設計「貓咪友善住宅」，辦公環境中到處可見悠哉步行的貓咪，甚至還有為毛孩們打造的專門走秀舞台，這個令人羨慕的工作場域在網路上爆紅，吸引不少鏟屎官們關注紛紛直呼「太羨慕！」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>根據外媒報導，這家不動產公司因應工作需求，需要經常觀察貓咪在室內的行為模式，因此收養了多隻貓咪作為「實地研究夥伴」，也鼓勵員工帶自家貓咪一起上班，長久下來讓公司辦公室逐漸成為了名副其實的貓奴天堂。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-231299" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/odya-kun-jXqvVxrtmdg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">這間公司內收養了許多貓咪，同時也鼓勵員工帶著自家愛貓一同上班<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>公司不僅有完善的活動空間，還設有多個貓跳台、窗邊觀景點與藏身角落，方便貓咪自由探索與休息，其中最受矚目的地方莫過於窗邊的狹長通道，這裡不僅是陽光灑落的地方，也是貓咪們最愛的散步小徑，每天不定時都會有幾隻貓優雅地穿越窗邊，像極了正在走秀的模特兒。&nbsp;</p>



<p>貓咪們的可愛行為讓整間辦公室瞬間充滿療癒氛圍，消息曝光後吸引許多貓奴們的熱烈討論，不少人紛紛表示「請問公司還有缺人嗎？」、「這才是夢想中的上班地點」、「員工一定超幸福」、「拜託錄取我吧」、「太羨慕了」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/24/%e8%b2%93%e5%a5%b4%e5%80%91%e7%9a%84%e5%a4%a2%e5%b9%bb%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%ef%bc%9f%e5%9c%a8%e9%80%99%e8%a3%a1%e4%b8%8a%e7%8f%ad%e7%ab%9f%e8%83%bd%e4%ba%ab%e5%8f%97%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9%e8%a2%ab%e8%b2%93/">貓奴們的夢幻公司？在這裡上班竟能享受整天被貓咪包圍！ </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
